is considered a complex blood problem. As the blood is thick, the blood flow in the small blood vessels of the body may be stopped.","title":"COVID-19 infected in Birgunj treated with plasma therapy - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/31/123966/","video":[]}
